General.Name: Austco Healthcare Ltd
General.Description: Austco Healthcare Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture, distribution, marketing, supply, service, and sale of healthcare and electronic communications systems in Australia, New Zealand, Asia, Europe, and North America. It offers Tacera, an IP system, and Medicom cost-effective solution for nurse call system; and Pulse Mobile, a native app for iOS and android devices. The company was formerly known as Azure Healthcare Limited and changed its name to Austco Healthcare Limited in November 2020. Austco Healthcare Limited was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Port Melbourne, Australia.
